cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.NE, cs.MM 

This paper is primarily focused on computer vision (CV) and machine learning (LG) techniques for image instance retrieval. The paper also discusses information retrieval (IR) and neural networks (NE) in the context of their proposed method. Additionally, the paper uses moments (MM) as a mathematical tool for their approach. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.CV and cs.LG, followed by cs.IR, cs.NE, and cs.MM.
